    Record that represents a 4D double vector.

    Class that represents an N-dimensional double vector.

    Record that represents a 4D float vector.

    Class that represents an N-dimensional float vector.

    Record that represents a 2D integer vector.

    Record that represents a 3D integer vector.

    Class that represents an N-dimensional integer vector.
    VectorAsDouble<D extends VectorDoubleOperations<D>>
    Interface to be implemented by a vector that can be represented as a double vector without casting.
    VectorAsFloat<F extends VectorFloatOperations<F>>
    Interface to be implemented by a vector that can be represented as a float vector without casting.
    VectorDoubleOperations<D extends VectorDoubleOperations<D>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for double vectors.
    VectorFloatOperations<F extends VectorFloatOperations<F>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for any float vector.
    VectorIntOperations<I extends VectorIntOperations<I>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for integer vectors.
    VectorMathException
    Thrown when an application attempts to perform an undefined operation with vectors.
    VectorOperations<V extends VectorOperations<V>>
    Base interface implemented by all vector types.
